## Evaluated and Rejected (this run)
- mitchellh/mapstructure (Go): Archived, but go-viper/mapstructure is active maintained fork.
- PLY/SLY (Python): Both archived, 61.5M dl/mo, but done software with declining use. Too complex for replacement value.
- pycparser (Python): Now actively maintained (v3.0 released Jan 2026).
- decorator (Python): Actively maintained (v5.2.1 Feb 2025).
